import os
import platform

def get_device_info():
    info = {
        "OS": platform.system(),
        "OS Version": platform.version(),
        "Machine": platform.machine(),
        "Processor": platform.processor(),
        "Python Version": platform.python_version()
    }
    return info

device_info = get_device_info()
for key, value in device_info.items():
    print(f"{key}: {value}")
